/** \brief Keyboard scan codes
  * Keyboard scan codes reflect the physical location of individual keys on a keyboard.
  * The keys may be labelled differently depending on the currently active keyboard layout.
  * These keyboard scan codes are based on the <a href="http://www.usb.org/developers/docs/">USB specification</a>.
  * \see KeyCode
  * \intern
  * The list of scan codes is based on SDL_scancode.h (SDL v2.0.8).
  */
